    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "See [this tweet](https://twitter.com/vdWijden/status/1529895417881800714) for info on how to get a Ropsten client to sync.\r\nTL;DR: you can use `--override.terminaltotaldifficulty 100000000000000000000000` to allow your client to start to sync again and you can run `debug.setHead(\"0xBBCE88\")` in [the console](https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interface/javascript-console) to sync the right blockchain.",
